      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Cecilia Hendricks" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Cecilia Hendricks" href="/user/show/33433327-cecilia-hendricks">Cecilia Hendricks</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1137120071" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3504879950697831227">This is undoubtedly one of the most intense things that I&apos;ve ever read. It was highly intelligent and informative. It helped me see the Russian Revolution in greater detail. But man alive, this was a mighty endeavor. It was a hard but good read. </span>
  <span id="freeText3504879950697831227" style="display:none">This is undoubtedly one of the most intense things that I've ever read. It was highly intelligent and informative. It helped me see the Russian Revolution in greater detail. But man alive, this was a mighty endeavor. It was a hard but good read. </span>
